---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Sympathy & Funeral Flowers in Essex | SB Floristry" 
  description="Elegant, respectful, and bespoke funeral flowers and sympathy tributes. Let the mother-daughter team at SB Floristry help you say farewell with grace."
>
  <!-- SEO Structured Data -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "Service",
      "serviceType": "Sympathy and Funeral Floristry",
      "provider": {
        "@type": "LocalBusiness",
        "name": "SB Floristry",
        "address": {
          "@type": "PostalAddress",
          "addressLocality": "Romford",
          "addressRegion": "Essex",
          "addressCountry": "UK"
        }
      },
      "description": "Respectful and bespoke funeral flowers, casket sprays, wreaths, and sympathy tributes hand-delivered in Essex."
    }
  </script>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative h-[70vh] overflow-hidden bg-sb-black">
      <div class="absolute inset-0">
          <img src="/images/collection-sympathy.jpg" alt="Elegant Sympathy Wreath" class="w-full h-full object-cover hero-zoom opacity-80" style="object-position: center 40%;">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1/3 bg-gradient-to-t from-sb-cream to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6 h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center text-sb-cream pt-20">
          <span class="text-sb-gold text-[10px] md:text-xs tracking-[0.35em] uppercase font-bold mb-4 reveal">Sympathy & Remembrance</span>
          <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-7xl mb-6 font-light reveal">Farewell with Grace</h1>
      </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Introduction Text -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-sb-cream transition-colors duration-500">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl">
           <div class="text-center reveal border-b border-gray-200 pb-16">
              <i class="fas fa-dove text-sb-gold text-2xl mb-6"></i>
              <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed">
                  We deeply understand the importance of saying goodbye beautifully. During this difficult time, our mother and daughter team provides a gentle, supportive service to help you choose the perfect tribute. Using the freshest seasonal blooms, we create arrangements that express your condolences and celebrate a life well-lived when words are simply not enough.
              </p>
           </div>
      </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tributes Collection -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-sb-cream">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl">
           <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-12 mb-24">
               
               <!-- Card 1 -->
               <div class="group flex flex-col items-center text-center reveal border border-gray-100 p-10 bg-white hover:border-sb-gold/50 transition-colors duration-500" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
                   <div class="w-16 h-px bg-sb-gold mb-8"></div>
                   <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl text-sb-black mb-4">Casket Sprays</h3>
                   <p class="text-gray-500 font-light mb-8 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
                       Elegant, double-ended sprays designed to sit perfectly atop the casket. Available in various sizes, we can tailor the color palette and flower selection to include favorite blooms or meaningful shades.
                   </p>
                   <span class="text-sb-gold text-[10px] tracking-luxury uppercase font-bold">From £150</span>
               </div>

               <!-- Card 2 -->
               <div class="group flex flex-col items-center text-center reveal border border-gray-100 p-10 bg-white hover:border-sb-gold/50 transition-colors duration-500" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
                   <div class="w-16 h-px bg-sb-gold mb-8"></div>
                   <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl text-sb-black mb-4">Wreaths & Hearts</h3>
                   <p class="text-gray-500 font-light mb-8 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
                       Traditional circular wreaths symbolizing eternal life, or beautifully crafted heart-shaped tributes representing enduring love. Hand-made meticulously with fresh moss bases and seasonal foliage.
                   </p>
                   <span class="text-sb-gold text-[10px] tracking-luxury uppercase font-bold">From £65</span>
               </div>

               <!-- Card 3 -->
               <div class="group flex flex-col items-center text-center reveal border border-gray-100 p-10 bg-white hover:border-sb-gold/50 transition-colors duration-500" style="transition-delay: 300ms;">
                   <div class="w-16 h-px bg-sb-gold mb-8"></div>
                   <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl text-sb-black mb-4">Posies & Baskets</h3>
                   <p class="text-gray-500 font-light mb-8 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
                       Delicate, thoughtful arrangements perfect as a gesture of sympathy for the home, for family members to contribute, or for graceful grave-side placement.
                   </p>
                   <span class="text-sb-gold text-[10px] tracking-luxury uppercase font-bold">From £45</span>
               </div>

               <!-- Card 4 -->
               <div class="group flex flex-col items-center text-center reveal border border-gray-100 p-10 bg-white hover:border-sb-gold/50 transition-colors duration-500" style="transition-delay: 400ms;">
                   <div class="w-16 h-px bg-sb-gold mb-8"></div>
                   <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl text-sb-black mb-4">Bespoke Tributes</h3>
                   <p class="text-gray-500 font-light mb-8 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
                       Personalized floral letters (such as MUM, DAD, or names), and custom shapes that reflect the unique personality, passions, and hobbies of your loved one.
                   </p>
                   <span class="text-sb-gold text-[10px] tracking-luxury uppercase font-bold">Price on Application</span>
               </div>

           </div>
      </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process / Reassurance Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-[#f2f0eb]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl text-center reveal">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl text-sb-black mb-10 font-light">Our Promise To You</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left mb-16">
              <div>
                  <h4 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-luxury font-bold text-sb-gold mb-3">1. Consultation</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">We offer a compassionate space to discuss your requirements, either over the phone or at our studio, moving at a pace that is entirely comfortable for you.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                  <h4 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-luxury font-bold text-sb-gold mb-3">2. Artistry</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">Every tribute is hand-crafted by us personally, ensuring the highest level of care, respect, and botanical artistry goes into honoring your loved one.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                  <h4 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-luxury font-bold text-sb-gold mb-3">3. Delivery</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">We liaise directly with your chosen local Funeral Director in Essex, ensuring seamless, timely, and respectful delivery of all floral tributes on the day.</p>
              </div>
          </div>
          
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-luxury border border-sb-black text-sb-black px-12 py-4 uppercase tracking-luxury text-xs font-bold inline-block hover:text-white">
              Contact Us To Discuss
          </a>
      </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
